Welcome to Zoe's Hangout living on the Polygon Blockchain and swimming in the OpenSea.  
  
You are invited to join our [Discord](https://discord.gg/Liuccio#3949), and follow us on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/LiuccioPhotos) or [Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/liuccio.photos/) for the latest updates, giveaways and news about Zoe's Hangout!  
---  
  
Your NFT metadata is hosted on the [IPFS](https://ipfs.io/) distributed web with a unique CID that you can find in the beginning of this description. We are also working with [Pinata](https://pinata.cloud/) as pinning tool to assure that your NFT Metadata will be on IPFS forever and no risk to lose it. You can know more about the advantage of having your NFT Metadata on IPFS with Pinata at [Medium](https://medium.com/pinata/the-file-requirements-for-nfts-a20ea3ac524b)
